Reasoning: The paper focuses on the development of a computer vision package for building segmentation and outline extraction, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The package also implements deep learning algorithms, which suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the package is evaluated using an aerial image dataset, which could potentially place it under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. Finally, the package includes utility scripts for model training and evaluation, which could also suggest that it belongs to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category.
